<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Liens_externes">Liens externes</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Sheldon_Glashow&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=10" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" title="Modifier la section : Liens externes">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Sheldon_Glashow&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Modifier la section : Liens externes">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
